    <title>Template:Jira</title>
    <revision>
      <model>wikitext</model>
      <format>text/x-wiki</format>
      <text>&lt;noinclude&gt;Links to Jira issues and queries via interwiki links.
* Use &lt;code&gt;{{Jira|key=PROJECT-123}}&lt;/code&gt; to link to a specific issue (uses the &lt;code&gt;jira-task&lt;/code&gt; interwiki prefix).
* Use &lt;code&gt;{{Jira|jql=...}}&lt;/code&gt; to link to a Jira filter. When the value is a Jira URL, the view type is detected from the path:
** &lt;code&gt;/timeline&lt;/code&gt; &#x2192; &lt;code&gt;jira-timeline&lt;/code&gt;
** &lt;code&gt;/calendar&lt;/code&gt; &#x2192; &lt;code&gt;jira-calendar&lt;/code&gt;
** &lt;code&gt;/summary&lt;/code&gt; &#x2192; &lt;code&gt;jira-summary&lt;/code&gt;
** &lt;code&gt;/boards&lt;/code&gt; &#x2192; &lt;code&gt;jira-board&lt;/code&gt;
** otherwise &#x2192; &lt;code&gt;jira-jql&lt;/code&gt; (plain JQL query)
&lt;/noinclude&gt;&lt;includeonly&gt;{{#if:{{{key|}}}|[[jira-task:{{{key}}}]]|{{#if:{{#pos:{{{jql|}}}|/timeline}}|[[jira-timeline:{{{jql}}}]]|{{#if:{{#pos:{{{jql|}}}|/calendar}}|[[jira-calendar:{{{jql}}}]]|{{#if:{{#pos:{{{jql|}}}|/summary}}|[[jira-summary:{{{jql}}}]]|{{#if:{{#pos:{{{jql|}}}|/boards}}|[[jira-board:{{{jql}}}]]|[[jira-jql:{{{jql}}}]]}}}}}}}}}}&lt;/includeonly&gt;
</text>
    </revision>
  </page>
